{"tid":1418224,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] ‘屎’攻嘅好處","createTime":"2019-08-05T18:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:42.000Z","uid":299712,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4dfbb65ae5b186fd16af6394c8c465dace034207","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:08:02.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次出post 請見諒<br />\n想讚下今日 &lsquo;<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>屎</strong></span>&rsquo;攻嘅朋友<br />\n<br />\n因為&lsquo;屎&rsquo;攻好多好處<br />\n<br />\n1. <ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">輿論</span></ins><br />\n扔屎好難定性攻擊性武器，政府都唔敢講自己比人扔。<br />\n就算敢講，都比人笑撚死。譴責我地扔屎？？？？<br />\n<br />\n2.<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">方便，成本低</span></ins><br />\n屎到處都有，又無成本，人人都可以成為法師。<br />\n附近街坊參戰又可以容易進行補給。<br />\n<br />\n3.<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">戰略作用</span></ins><br />\n當popo起左個popo line，我地就係佢地前面整個poopoo line。<br />\n屎可以令路面變得滑(爛屎更佳)，可以減慢popo進攻的時間。<br />\n<br />\n4.<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">心理壓</span>力</ins><br />\n你老母平時比人我地屌已經好容易嬲，如果中埋屎，我睇班popo仲唔立即崩潰。<br />\n平時我地扔雞蛋，就算黐住係個盾到都無咩野。<br />\n如果係屎，會不停散發濃烈的氣味(爛屎更佳)。<br />\n我唔信佢地會聞唔到，就算真係聞唔到。<br />\n都可以令佢地覺得自己「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">身有屎</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唯一我地要克服屎味先！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">目標：令佢地心理唔平衡<br />\n建議：先完成poopoo line 再扔屎去</span></span>popo到<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位討論！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"98109620be4a0041fd413c633dcff6c20e0ce621","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca22c70fd56db4ca93db9d9573780e4e87ed5de3","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d4a8de5ee4f885ea7019fa622794565bfc8f69d","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e42d8a531399a079503e3af2f5d41550afbbb96a","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:13:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73255163b48ce8456413b6f461fc80cd58a11091","tid":1418224,"uid":299712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"639e67ff04aaf82c139f8a090c908c87453b45f3","tid":1418224,"uid":115660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:14:56.000Z","msg":"（連仔入）強烈要求取消P牌正負評<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1418029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1418029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c06aa705e0f39cf492bba38045e6ab7d20e713b9","tid":1418224,"uid":220174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:15.000Z","msg":"輿論先屌得你甘<br />\n大眾: 好玩唔玩玩屎<br />\n民意係好重要咖"},{"pid":"34c79f587c356a5978d365c049ec191bce83c45d","tid":1418224,"uid":529,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 你諗住次次出發都帶盒屎係身定現場即刻痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"745cb8054740c17dd2aefcf03e1f2ee9e08a3967","tid":1418224,"uid":96799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34c79f587c356a5978d365c049ec191bce83c45d","tid":1418224,"uid":529,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"好奇一問 你諗住次次出發都帶盒屎係身定現場即刻痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ba1e96e802aaa6abfa986b7fad05b5e299ec10","tid":1418224,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:16:44.000Z","msg":"推一下咁大把啦<br />\n<br />\n但<br />\n如果係即場供給或者有難度，<br />\n如果事先準備又自己先而心理壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你話你樓下有班狗半夜吠好煩，就咁痾完掉落街又唔同講法"},{"pid":"487d498c904bb4898c43c81aa08faff1aaa7317b","tid":1418224,"uid":279995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:02.000Z","msg":"點帶出嚟？"},{"pid":"87b1a348fce7d129faa138118bd56299e8e21562","tid":1418224,"uid":294142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T18:18:42.000Z","msg":"求史偉莎借一架吸屎車"}]}